What else? Kevin, how are you?

01:06:07.826 --> 01:06:10.740
Yogi: Sorry, Shri Mataji…
Shri Mataji: Hot? Very hot?

01:06:10.941 --> 01:06:16.158
Yogi: No, I was late, I didn’t have time
to change my clothes.

01:06:16.359 --> 01:06:19.131
Shri Mataji: You are all right!

01:06:23.932 --> 01:06:26.175
You are all right.

01:06:26.386 --> 01:06:31.601
You see, when the Mother has seen you
in your “birthday suits”

01:06:31.802 --> 01:06:38.274
why should you worry about any dress
with your Mother, isn’t it?

01:06:41.065 --> 01:06:45.365
There is no formality with the Mother.

01:06:45.565 --> 01:06:47.646
It’s all right, She likes to see you
properly clad,

01:06:47.846 --> 01:06:51.811
but there’s nothing, no formality.

01:06:52.012 --> 01:06:55.645
[Aside, to somebody:] Thank you, that’s
all, thank you very much.

01:06:56.154 --> 01:06:58.205
[To the yogi] But you look serious, that’s
what I want to know.

01:06:58.405 --> 01:07:02.488
Yogi: Oh, I’m worried whether the Divine
is coming through on the tape.

01:07:02.689 --> 01:07:04.550
Shri Mataji: Oh, I see.
Yogi: Because I don’t know!

01:07:04.751 --> 01:07:09.200
Shri Mataji: Yes, I was wondering what’s
the matter, why are you so serious –

01:07:09.400 --> 01:07:14.380
no, I just thought, maybe because now
you are married

01:07:14.581 --> 01:07:19.226
and you are thinking of a married life now,

01:07:20.274 --> 01:07:26.045
what to do, and - No? No problems?
Yogi: No, no.

01:07:26.971 --> 01:07:29.997
Shri Mataji: You see, when you even tell
somebody, “You have to get married”,

01:07:30.198 --> 01:07:36.448
suddenly they … as if somebody has stuck
a pistol!

01:07:36.649 --> 01:07:41.850
That’s the first reaction I have seen
many-a-times.

01:07:42.051 --> 01:07:45.506
Pat has not come today? Yogini: No, Grazyna
is not very well, Mother.

01:07:45.707 --> 01:07:48.914
Shri Mataji: Hmm?
Yogini: Grazyna is still not very well...

01:07:49.115 --> 01:07:50.943
Shri Mataji: I know, poor thing.

01:07:51.143 --> 01:07:56.073
Yogini: They’d like to come and see You
next week…

01:07:56.542 --> 01:08:00.343
Shri Mataji: I have told - her problem
is basically something different,

01:08:00.543 --> 01:08:04.622
and I have told the solution and I’ve asked
Gavin, Gavin to find out.

01:08:04.823 --> 01:08:07.848
Did you ask Sarah?
Gavin: I didn’t get the chance just yet.

01:08:08.049 --> 01:08:12.145
Shri Mataji: But Sarah is here, you can
talk to her.

01:08:12.346 --> 01:08:18.383
You see, we have a, we had a doctor
in India called Dr. Shirolkar,

01:08:18.584 --> 01:08:21.007
and he devised an operation – you might
have heard his name

01:08:21.207 --> 01:08:22.706
[Yogini comments probably on name,
Shri Mataji: “Ah”] –

01:08:22.907 --> 01:08:27.981
to strengthen the … - Who is crying
so much?

01:08:28.181 --> 01:08:30.283
Just see the child -

01:08:30.502 --> 01:08:35.728
the lower wall, the lower wall of
the uterus, you see?

01:08:35.929 --> 01:08:39.167
And that operation somebody must be
doing here also, I’m sure.

01:08:39.368 --> 01:08:43.298
Yogini: Yes, she had it. Shri Mataji: Eh?
Yogini: She had it done.

01:08:43.561 --> 01:08:47.984
Shri Mataji: She had that operation?
Yogini: She did, but it’s still… she still…

01:08:48.192 --> 01:08:51.006
Shri Mataji: No, but then she conceived
very early then. [Yogini: “Sorry?”]

01:08:51.207 --> 01:08:55.406
You have to wait after that to develop
into a proper…

01:08:55.607 --> 01:09:00.085
she had that kind of an operation, did she?
Yogini: I think she did it, yes.

01:09:01.204 --> 01:09:04.211
Shri Mataji: Then she should have waited
to see that the wall is fully developed,

01:09:04.411 --> 01:09:11.177
I think if she had allowed to - I’m going
to work out something else for her.

01:09:12.872 --> 01:09:18.794
You can have another layer just to make it
strong, you see? [Yogini: “Yes.”]

01:09:28.121 --> 01:09:31.301
Any other problems?

01:09:37.484 --> 01:09:43.565
[To a yogini] How are you now? Gail?
All right?

01:09:47.424 --> 01:09:49.325
Don’t do any heavy work, but walking
is good.

01:09:49.526 --> 01:09:52.694
In Regent Park, you can go in the morning
for a walk, not in (unclear word)

01:09:52.895 --> 01:09:56.572
but it’s a good place to walk about
little bit.

01:09:56.773 --> 01:09:59.180
[To another yogini] How are you? Why don’t
you sit on a chair,

01:09:59.381 --> 01:10:03.812
will be better, better. Better sit down
on a chair.

01:10:04.013 --> 01:10:08.942
Go. Go there, to sit down.

01:10:11.205 --> 01:10:14.494
So how are you? [Yogini: “I’m all right…” ]
Good.

01:10:14.695 --> 01:10:20.891
I’m happy you could come. I’m happy
you could come.

01:10:27.034 --> 01:10:31.257
Received any letter? He is telephoning me,

01:10:31.458 --> 01:10:36.510
he is telling me that he is trying to get
the permission and this and that,

01:10:36.711 --> 01:10:39.872
he’s going to write to me again. His style
is like this.

01:10:40.081 --> 01:10:48.215
You see, he doesn’t want to talk about it
unless he really gets the permission.

01:10:48.557 --> 01:10:52.140
Yogini: I wrote to him.
Shri Mataji: You've written to him, yes.

01:10:52.379 --> 01:10:55.589
He telephones to me.

01:11:02.311 --> 01:11:07.851
All suspiciousness, you see, because he is
in the Air Force,

01:11:08.052 --> 01:11:11.259
and the government is suspicious
of foreigners, you see,

01:11:11.460 --> 01:11:16.966
marrying any Air Force this thing, you see.

01:11:18.586 --> 01:11:21.870
I just don’t understand.

01:11:22.807 --> 01:11:25.579
So I would say take my passport, you have
to walk like a criminal

01:11:25.780 --> 01:11:27.865
with your passport number, this, that,

01:11:28.066 --> 01:11:32.771
and you have to get my visas in Rome
and these places.

01:11:32.972 --> 01:11:36.711
But I think he can do it, Dinesh knows
how to do it.

01:11:36.912 --> 01:11:38.973
Tell him to go to Varad, Varad Rajan,

01:11:39.174 --> 01:11:43.321
he’ll give him, because is a diplomatic
passport.

01:11:52.163 --> 01:11:56.820
How are you now, Kay, are you better? Hm.

01:12:00.487 --> 01:12:03.987
Bala, what about your chickenpox?

01:12:05.543 --> 01:12:09.122
Gone?
Bala: It’s gone.

01:12:11.814 --> 01:12:14.851
Shri Mataji: Djamel, how are you?

01:12:16.494 --> 01:12:21.444
Djamel: I’ve got the Agnya problem.
Shri Mataji: Agnya?

01:12:30.903 --> 01:12:35.675
On the day of Resurrection Agnya should
clear out.

01:12:35.914 --> 01:12:40.164
Somebody has done everything for us, you
see? Best is to rely on that, all done!

01:12:40.365 --> 01:12:43.959
What, so why should we worry?

01:12:46.281 --> 01:12:49.071
Hm, better.

01:12:50.873 --> 01:12:54.003
Hm. Everything is done for you,

01:12:54.204 --> 01:12:57.824
I mean, lucky people I must say.

01:12:58.025 --> 01:13:02.600
Like guests, you see? That till, all
others have to do everything for you,

01:13:02.801 --> 01:13:06.627
and you have the fruits of it. Isn’t it?
A good situation.

01:13:06.828 --> 01:13:14.103
But still you look so worried.

01:13:17.017 --> 01:13:23.107
As we say, there’s a dog walking under
a cart.

01:13:23.323 --> 01:13:29.105
He looks very worried because he thinks
he is carrying the cart, you see.

01:13:29.306 --> 01:13:37.162
And the poor – the one, one, the bullocks
which are pulling the cart are quite happy.

01:13:43.120 --> 01:13:45.980
Better now?

01:13:47.950 --> 01:13:54.226
Is it true that in Islam they hate dogs?
Yogi: No, Mother.

01:13:54.427 --> 01:13:58.962
Shri Mataji: No? No. They don’t hate dogs.

01:13:59.163 --> 01:14:04.719
In Iran they – I don’t know why they hate
dogs so much.

01:14:04.922 --> 01:14:08.646
Somebody was telling me that they ill-treat
dogs, absolutely.

01:14:08.847 --> 01:14:12.014
I said, “Surprising it is.”
Yogi: Same in Malaysia.

01:14:12.215 --> 01:14:14.498
Shri Mataji: Hm? Yogi: They are not well
treated, animals in general

01:14:14.699 --> 01:14:16.375
are not well treated.
Shri Mataji: They?

01:14:16.576 --> 01:14:20.919
Yogi: They are very badly treated, You
know? Shri Mataji: Badly treated.

01:14:21.143 --> 01:14:27.632
Because, you see, they have become little
insensitive to animals, I think so.

01:14:27.834 --> 01:14:30.870
Like here people treat the dogs very
kindly,

01:14:31.071 --> 01:14:34.974
but their children very unkindly.
Is the other way round.

01:14:35.175 --> 01:14:39.400
I mean, it’s - just don’t understand, it’s
a mystery as I said.

01:15:02.342 --> 01:15:05.058
Those who want to see me, can come.

01:15:05.259 --> 01:15:10.514
Tomorrow evening I’ll be at home.

01:15:12.371 --> 01:15:14.835
All right?

01:15:16.463 --> 01:15:19.689
About, say, six o’clock.

01:15:20.071 --> 01:15:25.298
Then Sahasrara Puja must be fixed in the
evening, so that everybody can make it.

01:15:25.499 --> 01:15:29.604
Say about seven o’clock, that would be
good.

01:15:29.805 --> 01:15:35.126
Many people can come there – evening
because it’s a Wednesday or something.

01:15:35.358 --> 01:15:39.511
It’s a Wednesday? [Gavin: “Yes”] So Tuesday-
Wednesday Thursday- Friday, perhaps?

01:15:39.712 --> 01:15:43.165
Gavin: No, it’s a Wednesday.
Shri Mataji: It’s a Wednesday?

01:15:43.857 --> 01:15:45.947
Are you sure?

01:15:46.147 --> 01:15:49.021
Because if second is Tuesday…
Gavin: No, second is Sunday.

01:15:49.222 --> 01:15:52.294
Shri Mataji: Hm? Second is Tuesday.
Gavin: No, it’s Sunday.

01:15:52.495 --> 01:15:55.790
Shri Mataji: Is a Sunday. Then it’s all
right, Wednesday.

01:15:55.991 --> 01:16:00.932
So one should try to have it about seven
o’clock,

01:16:01.133 --> 01:16:04.076
so that others can come in for the puja.

01:16:04.277 --> 01:16:07.845
Now, is it over? Or…

01:16:09.036 --> 01:16:12.681
Yogi: … John Glower is here, and he’s
supposed to be …

01:16:12.882 --> 01:16:16.190
Shri Mataji: Where is he?

01:16:18.465 --> 01:16:21.726
So we can start the puja business because
otherwise it will get very late.

01:16:21.927 --> 01:16:27.152
All right? [Yogi: “Yes.”] When you, when
you get it…

01:16:27.379 --> 01:16:31.523
Yogi: …called Sahaja. Sahaja comes from
Indian language and it means

01:16:31.724 --> 01:16:35.403
“born with you”, or “spontaneous”, because
essentially Yoga

01:16:35.604 --> 01:16:39.323
isn’t just something that allows to keep
fit as has become in the West now.

01:16:39.524 --> 01:16:43.052
Yoga means union, union of your Self and
your Spirit,

01:16:43.253 --> 01:16:50.345
or of your Spirit and the Great Spirit,
which is the Divine, or God (…).

01:16:50.546 --> 01:16:54.504
And in that in fact your Spirit – which
again people nowadays

01:16:54.705 --> 01:16:56.813
don’t even know exists, most of them
usually feel embarrassed

01:16:57.014 --> 01:17:00.212
when you talk about souls and Spirit,
in fact is a reality.

01:17:00.436 --> 01:17:04.499
It is that within which is the true nature,

01:17:04.700 --> 01:17:10.242
its qualities are pure bliss, pure
consciousness and truth.

01:17:10.443 --> 01:17:15.887
And if one can experience that Spirit
consciously, then obviously

01:17:16.110 --> 01:17:19.045
one can be a very blissful person and not
have the problems that most people have.

01:17:19.246 --> 01:17:22.802
The question is: how do you get it? And
Sahaja means it is spontaneous,

01:17:23.010 --> 01:17:27.489
in other words something now for the first
time has made spontaneous

01:17:27.690 --> 01:17:33.173
Self-Realization, or knowing yourself fully
possible for the first time.

01:17:33.374 --> 01:17:35.259
Interviewer: You say “something”. Just
what is this something?

01:17:35.459 --> 01:17:40.550
Yogi: This something is the fact that in
the sacrum bone,

01:17:40.750 --> 01:17:44.927
which is the bone at the base of the spine,
is a being,

01:17:45.128 --> 01:17:48.536
that we call Kundalini, people in the East
call it as Kundalini.

01:17:48.736 --> 01:17:53.298
The Christians also have come across it,
but they called it Holy Spirit.

01:17:53.499 --> 01:17:55.890
Jesus has talked about it too. And …
Interviewer: The fact that the Christians

01:17:56.091 --> 01:17:58.536
that it is in the bone, they wouldn’t like.
Yogi: No, they wouldn’t, no, they wouldn’t

01:17:58.737 --> 01:18:01.199
but nevertheless Christ talked about it,
that’s the essential thing,

01:18:01.399 --> 01:18:05.270
not that the Christians would necessarily;
but rather what Christ said.

01:18:05.471 --> 01:18:13.429
Now, somehow this being, which is
the Divine inside,

01:18:13.630 --> 01:18:19.624
has to link up the individual Spirit - we
say the Atma, the personal Spirit -

01:18:19.825 --> 01:18:24.041
with the One, the Divine, right? And
the way that happens

01:18:24.242 --> 01:18:29.791
is that the Kundalini rises up the spine,
enlightens Spirit,

01:18:29.992 --> 01:18:34.164
and pierces – it goes to actually seven
subtle centres called chakras –

01:18:34.372 --> 01:18:36.778
which I will tell about in a minute if you
like –

01:18:36.979 --> 01:18:40.673
until it pierces the fontanel bone on top
of the head,

01:18:40.874 --> 01:18:42.967
this top chakra, the top center.

01:18:43.168 --> 01:18:46.360
When that happens, the personal spiritual
reality inside,

01:18:46.561 --> 01:18:49.251
which is the Spirit and the subtle centres
and the Kundalini,

01:18:49.452 --> 01:18:52.318
which is latent if you like Divine power
within,

01:18:52.519 --> 01:18:55.799
all are brought into the conscious nervous
system for the first time.

01:18:56.000 --> 01:18:58.978
Interviewer: If this is there, or has been
there all the time,

01:18:59.200 --> 01:19:00.891
why is it that it hasn’t happened before?
Yogi: Why it hasn’t happened before,

01:19:01.092 --> 01:19:03.433
well, it happened before in a few cases,

01:19:03.634 --> 01:19:07.222
there have been enlightened people who were
great saints,

01:19:07.423 --> 01:19:09.878
people with immense courage and spiritual
power

01:19:10.079 --> 01:19:11.937
who did have their Self-Realisation before,

01:19:12.137 --> 01:19:15.921
I mean you could say that Lord Buddha
was a man

01:19:16.129 --> 01:19:19.852
who, because of his great perfection,
attained his spiritual life,

01:19:20.053 --> 01:19:21.854
in other words the Kundalini came up fully,

01:19:22.055 --> 01:19:25.214
and he was totally as we’d say
God-realised, in other words

01:19:25.422 --> 01:19:28.952
he became a hollow personality flowing
as if played through, his ego just went,

01:19:29.153 --> 01:19:32.554
as well as his conditionings went, and he
was just as the Spirit.

01:19:32.770 --> 01:19:35.227
And now it happens to anybody, and this is
the main thing,

01:19:35.428 --> 01:19:38.295
this is the interesting, exciting and
thoroughly enjoyable thing;

01:19:38.496 --> 01:19:41.795
but now, it isn’t a case that just a few
sages go and live on a mountain

01:19:41.996 --> 01:19:43.976
in a pure, absolutely perfect knowledge

01:19:44.177 --> 01:19:47.651
may at the end of all [unclear] time
get their Self-Realisation:

01:19:47.852 --> 01:19:51.131
now, any of us who desire it, any of us
who are seeking it,

01:19:51.331 --> 01:19:53.881
genuine seekers can get their
Self-Realisation.

01:19:54.082 --> 01:19:57.361
And the reason for that is that an Indian
lady, called Mataji,

01:19:57.561 --> 01:19:59.913
Her Holiness Mataji Nirmala Devi,

01:20:00.114 --> 01:20:04.923
has come absolutely foremost to give
this gift of Self-Realisation,

01:20:05.131 --> 01:20:07.791
by which – not that She is a guru who has
come just to,

01:20:07.992 --> 01:20:11.129
you know, have people sit at Her feet,
and pay money and so on;

01:20:11.330 --> 01:20:13.731
on the contrary, She said you can’t pay
for the Divine,

01:20:13.932 --> 01:20:18.514
you can’t pay for your Yoga, your Union
with your Spirit and God.

01:20:18.715 --> 01:20:23.628
It happens spontaneously, and the reason
it happens, is because in Her presence

01:20:23.829 --> 01:20:28.439
vibrations which come from Her, or even
from the photograph of Her,

01:20:28.648 --> 01:20:31.465
come in through the upper side
of the hands,

01:20:31.666 --> 01:20:35.564
and that acts as a trigger for
the Kundalini which is residing,

01:20:35.765 --> 01:20:38.386
which as you say we don’t know about,
which may have been there –

01:20:38.587 --> 01:20:41.960
is there nevertheless whether we know
about it or not - at the base of the spine.

01:20:42.161 --> 01:20:44.805
This rises up and that cool breeze,

01:20:45.012 --> 01:20:46.672
what you feel as cool breeze in your hands,
all right?

01:20:46.873 --> 01:20:49.532
Vibrations flowing from Mataji
in full-fledged form –

01:20:49.733 --> 01:20:53.059
the Kundalini then comes up and you begin
to feel things in your…

01:20:53.260 --> 01:20:55.710
Interviewer: There are many people that - do you know that the real fact is,

01:20:55.911 --> 01:20:56.877
and I have to say this…
Yogi: Yes.

01:20:57.078 --> 01:20:59.153
Interviewer: …is that there are lots and
lots of people

01:20:59.353 --> 01:21:01.241
who are saying very similar types
of things;

01:21:01.465 --> 01:21:08.048
and also lots of people, let’s have it,
just… (indistinct words), you know.

01:21:08.249 --> 01:21:11.843
What’s the difference between this one
and the rest? Yogi: Right.

01:21:12.044 --> 01:21:13.703
There are lots of differences, but
admittedly,

01:21:13.904 --> 01:21:17.557
because of the age we’re living in, because
there are so many things around,

01:21:17.758 --> 01:21:23.170
some of which have been absolutely proved
by psychologists and other people,

01:21:23.371 --> 01:21:27.249
just intelligent people, to be absolutely
dangerous and damaging to people.

01:21:27.450 --> 01:21:29.683
That has to tell you the difference,
you have to have a discernment.

01:21:29.884 --> 01:21:33.353
Discernment, as I said beforehand is that
you have to judge Mataji,

01:21:33.553 --> 01:21:37.663
you have to judge Sahaja Yoga on what you
feel about it I suppose, right?

01:21:37.864 --> 01:21:40.708
Before your Realisation. And also using
consent.

01:21:40.947 --> 01:21:44.215
But Mataji’s message is this: you can’t pay
for the Divine, absolutely not,

01:21:44.416 --> 01:21:46.946
it’s satanic to try and pay for the Divine.

01:21:47.170 --> 01:21:50.563
Secondly, if a thing is genuine, you are
not going to get bad side effects,

01:21:50.764 --> 01:21:53.521
you are not going to feel ill: if a thing
is holy and is good and pure

01:21:53.722 --> 01:21:58.780
you’ll feel good; and it will be obvious in
your whole personality (indistinct words).

01:21:58.981 --> 01:22:01.799
And equally,

01:22:02.000 --> 01:22:06.656
you can’t come to this spiritual
Realisation, or God you could say,

01:22:06.857 --> 01:22:09.800
or your Spirit or the truth, you can’t come
to that

01:22:10.024 --> 01:22:14.030
on a path which is unrighteous, you can’t
come to that on a path

01:22:14.230 --> 01:22:19.762
of unholiness, of immorality, or
of extreme behaviour.

01:22:19.964 --> 01:22:23.124
Interviewer: But you know, there are lots
of others who tell exactly the same words.

01:22:23.325 --> 01:22:25.563
Then  what’s the difference between
yourselves and say Raja Yoga?

01:22:25.764 --> 01:22:27.128
Now they don’t get money either.

01:22:27.336 --> 01:22:29.107
Yogi: The fact is that we have the actual
happening,

01:22:29.307 --> 01:22:31.845
which you can feel inside yourself, you
feel the cool breeze.

01:22:32.046 --> 01:22:35.469
When you get Realisation, and anybody
gets it - you don’t have to pay for it -

01:22:35.670 --> 01:22:38.973
you feel the cool breeze in your hands
coming from the picture or from Mataji.

01:22:39.181 --> 01:22:41.207
As soon as you actually feel, and you have
to verify for yourself,

01:22:41.414 --> 01:22:43.993
and you might say “there’s a cool breeze”,
doesn’t make a cool breeze;

01:22:44.194 --> 01:22:46.741
but if you feel the cool breeze you can’t
really deny it.

01:22:46.942 --> 01:22:49.181
Secondly, you feel cool which comes out
of your head,

01:22:49.382 --> 01:22:51.588
when you get Realisation, not before.

01:22:51.789 --> 01:22:55.812
Thirdly, you begin to feel all this
extremely subtle, very sensitive

01:22:56.013 --> 01:23:00.836
and beautifully made creation which is
the human personality.

01:23:01.037 --> 01:23:04.468
You begin to feel its subtleties.
Interviewer: Where does this all lead us?

01:23:04.669 --> 01:23:07.662
Where is it going to take us? Yogi: It
takes us into the future, absolutely,

01:23:07.863 --> 01:23:11.054
or you could say into the present; it takes
you to yourself.

01:23:11.255 --> 01:23:15.551
When the Kundalini goes through the second
to the top chakra - the sixth chakra,

01:23:15.752 --> 01:23:17.846
you come into the present and you enter
a state

01:23:18.047 --> 01:23:20.570
of thoughtless awareness, spontaneously.
It’s absolutely natural,

01:23:20.771 --> 01:23:23.316
it just happens, when the Kundalini
reaches that point.

01:23:23.517 --> 01:23:30.599
The reason for that is that, suppose you
are thinking,

01:23:30.815 --> 01:23:34.804
you can’t possibly be in the present, you
can’t be aware of the actually present.

01:23:35.005 --> 01:23:37.367
You can be aware of just what’s just
passed,

01:23:37.568 --> 01:23:39.437
or what’s going to happen in a very short
time,

01:23:39.638 --> 01:23:41.885
but you can’t be aware of the absolute
present.

01:23:42.086 --> 01:23:45.406
So the only way to be in the present,
absolutely, is to be thoughtless,

01:23:45.607 --> 01:23:50.723
and the Kundalini does this, when it
crosses that point on the forehead.

01:23:50.924 --> 01:23:54.266
Then you just become thoughtlessly aware
and we are in that state all the time.

01:23:54.467 --> 01:23:57.606
All we do is in that state. It sounds
strange, but it’s a reality.

01:23:57.807 --> 01:24:00.580
The cares go, the troubles go, your
problems go, as these chakras

01:24:00.781 --> 01:24:03.361
get cleared out by the Kundalini rising up,

01:24:03.562 --> 01:24:06.319
it clears out all the awful things that
cause the problems;

01:24:06.520 --> 01:24:10.245
and you become in the end a joyful being.

01:24:10.446 --> 01:24:13.076
Interviewer: And should you be interested,
She is holding a meeting at Caxton Hall

01:24:13.277 --> 01:24:19.820
on Wednesday the fourteenth of April
at 7pm, everyone is welcome.

