Specially on Christ I spoke very well.

01:30:14.698 --> 01:30:22.003
And why don’t you send this one
to Houston people,

01:30:22.268 --> 01:30:25.824
the one on the Easter day, will be good
idea, you see?

01:30:26.040 --> 01:30:33.284
